query.formula: strategy safe = control:A[(!cps_i_state.detection.collide && !cps_i_state.detection.outside) U count == stage[NOW]]

query.comment: or "strategy safeReach = E<> control: A<> cps_i_state.detection.reach"

query.formula: strategy reach = maxE((5+100*cps_i_state.detection.reach)*rProgress) [<=MAXTIME]{controller.location, move.location, turn.location, cps_i_state.position.x, cps_i_state.position.y, cps_i_state.velocity, cps_i_state.orientation, cps_i_state.acceleration, cps_i_state.accRate, cps_i_state.yawRate, obs_i_state[0].position.x, obs_i_state[0].position.y, obs_i_state[0].velocity, obs_i_state[0].orientation, obs_i_state[1].position.x, obs_i_state[1].position.y, obs_i_state[1].velocity, obs_i_state[1].orientation, obs_i_state[2].position.x, obs_i_state[2].position.y, obs_i_state[2].velocity, obs_i_state[2].orientation, obs_i_state[3].position.x, obs_i_state[3].position.y, obs_i_state[3].velocity, obs_i_state[3].orientation}-> {}: <> cps_i_state.detection.reach
query.comment: strategy reachSafe = minE(cost) [<=MAXTIME] {control.location}->{cps_i_state.position.x, cps_i_state.position.y, cps_i_state.velocity, cps_i_state.orientation, cps_i_state.acceleration, cps_i_state.accRate, cps_i_state.yawRate, obs_i_state[0].position.x, obs_i_state[0].position.y, obs_i_state[0].velocity, obs_i_state[0].orientation, obs_i_state[1].position.x, obs_i_state[1].position.y, obs_i_state[1].velocity, obs_i_state[1].orientation}: <> g_time>=MAXTIME under safe

query.formula: simulate [<=MAXTIME;1] { cps_dynamic.x, cps_dynamic.y, cps_dynamic.orientation, cps_dynamic.velocity, cps_dynamic.acceleration }:cps_i_state.detection.reach under safeReach
